'''''Pediatric Clinics of North America''''' is a clinical [[healthcare journal| medical journal]] in [[pediatrics]] published by [[W. B. Saunders]], and imprint of [[Elsevier]].

== Abstracting and indexing ==
The journal is included in the following abstracting and indexing services: [[BIOSIS]],  [[CINAHL]], [[Current Contents]]/Clinical Medicine and Current Contents/Life Sciences,  [[EMBASE|Excerpta Medica]],  [[MEDLINE]], [[Reference Update]], and the [[Science Citation Index]].

